resources.string:
The game is supposed to improve your Sense of Bar™ by giving you an opportunity to click once a period. The game consists of three parts:
 in the first part you assign a duration in beats per minutes(the default interval is 120 bpm (half a second)); 
 in the second part the game starts (click on the screen once per period), and ends by pressing the big red button; 
 in the third part your results summarize. And remember: the longer you play, the more accurate your result.
